<BaseLayout title="About — Christian Blank" description="About Christian Blank — researcher, founder, and investor.">
  <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Christian Blank, based in Northern Germany. My work sits at the intersection of software
      engineering, machine learning research, and building companies.
    </p>

    <h2>Research</h2>
    <p>
      I studied computer engineering and computer science, and started my PhD at the University of
      Bremen in 2019. My research interests have shifted over the years — from gesture recognition
      and augmented reality toward testing methodologies for machine learning systems and AI agent safety.
      The central question I keep returning to: how do you verify the behavior of a system you cannot
      fully specify?
    </p>

    <h2>Companies</h2>
    <p>
      I'm the founder and managing director of <a href="https://lemonade-research.de">Lemonade Research GmbH</a>,
      a software and AI consultancy working with German Mittelstand companies.
      I also run <a href="https://cubicl.de">Cubicl GmbH</a>, which handles real estate investment and management.
    </p>
    <p>
      Current projects include <a href="https://wemate.de">Wemate</a> (a community platform),
      <a href="https://grundblick.de">Grundblick</a> (real estate analytics), and
      Lumi (an AI assistant infrastructure project).
    </p>

    <h2>This Blog</h2>
    <p>
      I write about things I'm actively thinking through — primarily AI safety, testing of learning
      systems, and the practical challenges of deploying intelligent software. These are working notes
      as much as polished arguments. If something is wrong, I want to know.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Best reached via <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/christian-blank-55b669195/">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
